title: HappyFood by YogaHub
typeOfFood: Vegan, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Provides gluten-free veggie breakfast, lunch, snacks, plus juices and smoothies. Vegan lunch/dinner specials every day. Hosts movie nights and events. After 4pm Mon-Fri, cafe is closed, but take away is available while yoga classes are happening. Sun open for teas/coffees and snacks only. July/Aug 2014 moved its cafe to inside a yoga studio; previously at Ferocious Mingle Marcade on Camden St. Reported all vegan Jan 2016.
